{"tid":1123242,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(92撚請入) 10年前嘅今日, 就係2009年會考主科正式開考","createTime":"2019-04-24T10:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T08:23:07.000Z","uid":52429,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4d91fc39a0525e9102e5bb957849cdb0755cde0c","tid":1123242,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pSbz5yc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpSbz5yc.jpg&h=5fcb3f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9nsC3jT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9nsC3jT.jpg&h=23b03a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2009年4月24日<br />\n中國語文科卷一及卷二 (閱讀及寫作能力) 正式開考<br />\n卷一: A-level中化科咁嘅野<br />\n卷二: Writing, 揀三題是但一題作<br />\n<br />\n1. 有朋自遠方來<br />\n2. 樓梯與升降機<br />\n3. 有人說：『與其追隨潮流，不如展現個人風格。』你對這句話有什麼看法？<br />\n<br />\n結果揀咗第2題向困難挑戰<br />\n之後我自己都唔知道作咗D咩<br />\n<br />\n10年前嘅今日, 各位喺邊個試場考?<br />\n當日喺北角蘇浙個Hall度考"},{"pid":"6b5c7132f3aa4a6a05fc22f1e1a6acebbdc4f783","tid":1123242,"uid":52429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb018b7cd764f95d664de2e54f3ce008488fc77f","tid":1123242,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdb81f73b424134ddf96315be01490820b3d54d","tid":1123242,"uid":52429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90562f355cbdccaf66c414eef30e426034e8b494","tid":1123242,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f070cf6cc5a11b5d6c6654efd8f0fcf219b086","tid":1123242,